  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      we evaluate the presence of OSA in patients that have a computed tomography (CT) of the chest
      to rule out pulmonary embolism (PE) to determine if OSA constitutes an independent risk
      factor for PE.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
